{"tid":1029432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實單程證要繼續實施","createTime":"2019-02-20T08:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T14:49:40.000Z","uid":50745,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cc1dbfa2f12978053cb554909f2c8b9b47e7ee","tid":1029432,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"不過係由香港送去大灣區<br />\n香港已經無乜發展空間<br />\n為左配合咁偉大既大灣區發展<br />\n大陸專才更加要去大灣區<br />\n咁先可以發揮到佢地既能力<br />\n政府講到新移民勞動力效率高<br />\n咁更加要將佢地送去大灣區<br />\n為偉大國家效力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大灣區既然好似政府講到咁好咁有潛力<br />\n一於實施香港到大灣區單程證<br />\n名額每日300<br />\n將大陸專才同新移民送上去<br />\n香港咁先叫有貢獻嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a763515183939f102a6c9343294f3b0fdb52c910","tid":1029432,"uid":50745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"大家集思廣益諗下點樣可以為國效力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03202d75c0e4c282022d7c03607a9ee125a31a2a","tid":1029432,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:50:30.000Z","msg":"雙程證取代先"},{"pid":"fa28a8abb271d2c56d0ebc7dc38ff9e6b89223f8","tid":1029432,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a63a31443be9f742f4e5d9de6d469622266a9b4","tid":1029432,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b2ac4f934af409811201cd5045a82f89b7b163","tid":1029432,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"D腥港人撚有技術生產力咩 落黎香港大部分都係做保安清潔果類散工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/